==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: no-see-um
<hw>no-see-um</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any of several
minute two-winged biting insects of the family
<fam>Ceratopogonidae</fam> that suck the blood of mammals and birds and
other insects; also called <altname>biting midge</altname> and
<altname>punkie</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> punkie, punky, punkey, biting midge.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nosegay</ent>⟦br⟧
